trong>eCho</strong> network with extinction. Propel through digital landscapes, crafting new break beats to infuse a stagnating network with the spark of renewal. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this <strong>Alpha-Demo</strong> players are granted access to the <strong>first two worlds</strong> of the opening story mode, averaging roughly 1-2 hours of gameplay. You will connect to the eCho network, develop your input capabilities with new combos and abilities, and learn how the game is structured. This Alpha-Demo is an opportunity to provide direct feedback to me (the developer) so that I can make the best possible full release. All reviews and feedback are encouraged!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246030/extras/image_160.png?t=1730674662\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">ANGEL imbues the flow state of racing with the complexity of breakbeat music enhanced by a soundtrack from MyraTV, and many other breakbeat enthusiasts. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As eCho faces its extinction, the ANGEL protocol - <strong>EXPLORE, CREATE, REFLECT</strong>- persists. Embark on a journey that questions what it means to be connected. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246030/extras/rememberechogif.gif?t=1730674662\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","developers":["Michael Hunter"],"fullgame":{"appid":"2884840","name":"Angel"},"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Racing","id":"9"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246030/header.jpg?t=1730674662","is_free":true,"legal_notice":"\u00a9 2024 Antidiscipline. All rights reserved. Published b